	<h2><a class="titles" href="./viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=4407&amp;start=60">Mega Man 9 - Feasible on NES?</a></h2>


	<p class="moderators">Moderator: <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=group&amp;g=320">Moderators</a></p>

</div>

<br clear="all" /><br />

